description:
A best pal for life, this crochet dog is tops.

A great toy to make a nursery or even the perfect gift for that special new born. 
These fabulous hand crochet toys will provide baby/ toddler with hours of entertainment and a friend for bed time.
Soft-to-hold and fun to cuddle, this dog makes a great gender neutral gift. 

Stripe dog is free standing approx 36.5cm long and 19.5cm tall. 

Colours are blue and cream stripe and he wears cute little hat.

name: Lambskin Booties
description:
We adore these Naturebaby booties made from lambskin with a luxuriously soft and fluffy inner. Warm, snuggly and excellent at staying on little feet.

Handmade in New Zealand
Also available in Cinnamon and Mustard.
0-3 months - 9cm 
3-6 months - 11cm 
6-12 months - 13cm

name: Memory Game - Charley Harper
description:
Great memory game for the whole family, featuring the iconic illustrations of Charley Harper. 

There are 36 pairs in total, but you can use less pairs in a game for younger children. 

Suitable for ages 2+

Box measures 19.5 x 19.5 x 2.5 cm

name: Handmade Kitty-Cat
description:
Do we spy a clowder of crocheted cats made by Wendy? (Clowder is the proper word for a group of kitties, did you know that? Now you do!) 

There are no buttons or detachable pieces, which makes these handmade friends ideal for all ages. They generally measure in at around 40cm from head to tail.

Choose your favourite colour, or collect them all!

name: Tiny Folk Shadow Puppets - 2 styles
description:
There are two themes to choose from, Fairytale and Moon. The puppets are laser cut from thick, high quality matboard, ideal for casting a strong shadow. Kids will spin tales and invent worlds, using just a lamp (or the sun) and their imagination.

Each set, $25, comes with a base and five puppets.

name: Special Bear by Margot
description:
These little bears are very dear to our hearts here at Shorties. Handknitted by 90 year old Margot, every bear is unique, and has his own personality. So special, and only $19 each.

Length: approx 16 cm

NOTE: Intended as decoration for children under 3, due to small buttons.

name: Helmets
description:
Here's either a dotty (nutty) classic to go with every colour in your wardrobe or on your bike! Or call all the shots with this 8 Ball, or just hope for luck!

They feature:
ABS injection hard shell
Unique Anti-Pinch Magnetic Buckle
Anti-rust rivets
360 degree reflectivity on Nutcase logos and buckles
Cool and shiny gloss surface
Special Nutcase-styled EVA Shock absorbing liner
Special 11 vents design for the perfect ventilation
Full surround interior for a great fit
Additional foam pad set in each box to customise your fit
Eco friendly packaging
Complies with Australian/NZ safety standards

name: Mini Micro Scooters
description:
Mini Micro Scooters are a great way to help develop balance, co-ordination and motor skills. Kids LOVE these scooters!

The original 3 wheel design combined with the lean and steer action ensures safety and stability for young children. It enables them to learn to use their body weight and balance to steer.

Features:
3 wheel design for stability 
Wide non-slip deck 
Low to the ground 
Quality non-marking wheels 
Suitable for indoors / outdoors 
Lean and steer action 
Removable handlebars 

Available in Pink, Blue, Orange, Red, Yellow and Green

Age Range: 2+ (pair with the micro kick seat - coming soon) for younger kids.
Max Load: 35kg* 
Scooter weighs: 1.5kg 

* Please not the bottom of the scooter shows a weight limit of 20kg, the Mini Micro is designed with a weight recommendation of 35kg. The reason for the difference: European standards dictate that weights are displayed as 20, 50 or 100kg.

name: ABC Book by Charley Harper
description:
"Ever since he was a young boy growing up on the farm, Charley Harper loved animals and enjoyed drawing and painting pictures of them. For over 60 years, Charley painted beautiful colourful and graphic pictures of animals and the world around him."

A classic ABC board book featuring the colourful wildlife illustrations of Charley Harper. Young children can learn their ABC's through the delightful and graphic images of animals created by American illustrator Charley Harper. This small gem is sure to become a classic, and is a beautifully designed and educational book for Harper fans, both young and old.

name: Hand Knitted Owl
description:
We adore these darling hand-knitted owls made by very talented knitter Rose. 

The tawny little critters usually measures in at around ----  and would be a beautiful gift for a brand new baby or owl enthusiast (and we know there are plenty of those). 

The joy of handmade toys is that no two are absolutely alike! Please be aware that the shades of your owl may vary ever so slightly from the one pictured here (all the owls are brown with yellow eyes). 

We can, of course, guarantee a special friend for years to come.

name: Bum Magic
description:
Australian author Claudia Rowe pays homage to an Australian classic. These cheeky book is actually very sweet, and will have any child giggling away. 

softcover, 32 pages
100% recycled paper
19x19cm

name: Cotton Yacht Shirt
description:
A lovely sunsafe shirt for summer days, from Aussie label Three Sun Possums. These 100% cotton shirts will keep your little possums safe from the harsh summer sun, and give them the freedom to hop, skip, run and play all through the holidays.

Lightweight, machine washable, and unisex, we just love the nautical yacht design!

Two colours, Navy or White.

name: Kembo Cuisenaire Set
description:
Remember Cuisenaire rods? These colourful little wooden sets were once used widely in schools to teach arithmetic and fractions, and they're still great all these years later.

These sets are Aussie made - Australian company Kembo have been making these Cuisenaire sets for 40 years. Legends! 

The rods are a fascinating learning tool for kids 3 and up, each kit contains 136 rods and a comprehensive instruction booklet.

name: Handmade Crochet Bags
description:
Little ones will love toting their trinkets around in one of these cute crochet handbags. 

Handmade in Sydney by crochet mastermind Mel, no two are exactly alike. 

The bags all feature a child-size strap, MEASURING, ideal for ages 2 and up. Available in four adorable designs:
Panda
Black Cat
Lion
Koala

name: La Tour des Robots
description:
Build and balance a robot tower with this wooden stacking puzzle from Vilac. There are so many ways to stack these little guys! This game makes for a fun and captivating activity for children aged 3 to 6.

Packaging measurements: 410g, 27 x 17cm

name: Space Hoppers
description:
Bounce away the day on a retro style space hopper!

We're so happy that these hoppers are made right here in Australia. The heavy duty design is sturdy and the perfect size for kids aged 3+

140mm circumference
weighs 400gm

Inflate with a standard bicycle pump. 
Comes boxed

name: Wooden Birthday Cake
description:
Kids just love these wooden Birthday cakes, complete with decorations and wooden birthday candles. Packaged in a 29 x 26 x 5cm pine box for storage and gifting.

Featuring velcro to stick all the pieces together, and wooden knife to 'cut' the cake, it's perfect for pretend play. Such fun!
 
Suitable for ages 3+ (contains small pieces)

name: Memory Game - Patrick Hruby
description:
Great memory game for the whole family, featuring bold, modern illustrations from artist Patrick Hruby. 

There are 36 pairs in total, but you can use less pairs in a game for younger children. 

Suitable for ages 2+

Box measures 19.5 x 19.5 x 2.5 cm

name: Click Clack Wooden Stations
description:
The Click Clack fire station, ambulance station and police station are easy to build and so much fun. Each has a garage with opening/closing door, a carport for an extra vehicle, and a helipad for your Click Clack helicopter (vehicles not included with station). 

Made from sustainable timber and 100% recycled plastic, and packaged in 100% recycled cardboard, Click Clack toys are the ethical choice for the little car fanatic in your life. 

Collect them all

name: Shorties Tee - Bird
description:
White cotton baby tees with popper stud on the neck, featuring a sweet and simple bird design.

These are great every day t-shirts: unisex, comfy and printed here in Sydney!

name: Zing Gliders
description:
Zing Gliders by Tiger Tribe really do fly like a bird and go like a rocket!
They can soar over 30 metres! 

Zing Gliders are extra strong and durable and feature a soft rubber protective nose so kids can use them and over and over again. 

This awesome toy always sells out, it's the perfect gift for ages 6+
(In our experience, dads love them too!)

Packaging measures 24 x 31.5 x 2 cm

name: Accordion
description:
It's a well established fact that an accordion will help you win friends and influence people. 

These delightful child-sized button accordions are a real instrument, and they sound fantastic. They're easy to operate too, so young children (and even hapless grown ups) will be able to squeeze out a tune.

name: Book - Foods Babies Love
description:
Food Babies Love is a beautiful collection of recipes for babies and children, written by mum of three, Emily Dupuche. 
As well as yummo recipes to take your baby from first solids through to childhood favourites, the book is filled with helpful tips and product recommendations.

This is the perfect gift for new parents, and for anyone who'd love to prepare fresh whole-foods for the whole family.

Softcover, 188 pages.

name: Knitted Toy - Kookaburra
description:
Laugh kookaburra laugh!
This gorgeous hand-knitted fellow was made by Rose, and features delicate stitched details. He would make a lovely gift to send overseas, a handmade friend to keep forever.

name: Cowboy Suit - Vest and Chaps
description:
Australian made cowboy costumer!
The retro design is perfect for imaginative play. 
Adjustable waist size means chaps can be worn over everyday pants, and can be made to fit most kids.

Length to suit to sizes (see below for details)

name: Handmade Millet Broom
description:
These beautiful child-size brooms are made by hand at the Tumut Broom Factory in country NSW. The sturdy yet soft millet bristles are perfect for little helpers! For indoor and outdoor use.

Broom measures approx. 80cm

name: Saltwater Sandals - Navy
description:
Kids just love these sandals! 

Saltwaters are known and loved for their retro charm, but the best thing about them is how comfortable they are. Made from high-quality leather and vulcanised rubber, they'll withstand a lot of summer fun. 

Sling them on for the beach or add a pretty frock and show them off at parties. Saltwaters love the sun, sea and sand as much as we do!

Please see the below menu for sizes.

name: Bath Sponges by Donkey - Rock Star
description:
Being captain of the tub day after day can quickly get boring. These fun kids' sponges can transform your youngsters into rockstars - and get them spotless on top of it.

Bathsponge / Microphone & Headphone
25 x 19 x 3 cm

name: Klippan Baby Blanket
description:
Swedish company Klippan have been making amazing textiles since 1879!

These soft 100% cotton chenille blankets are a beautiful and practical gift for new babies and new mothers. They're a great size for the cot, the pram, or as a baby rug.

The Friendly Monsters design by Lotta Glave is fun, quirky, and unisex too. It comes in green and black.

The Bruno Bear design is by Karin Mannerstal. We love it for it's cute, classic charm, and because it's suitable for both baby boys and baby girls. 

Measures 70 x 90 cm

name: The Stripey Street Cat
description:
The Stripey Street Cat is a locally produced book. While the authors didn't paint the graffiti, they have photographed a great collection of these Stripey Street Cats, and written a sweet story to compliment the accompanying urban legend.

A book for kids and grown ups alike - just beautiful.

Measures 12 x 17 cm

name: Scoops Brooches
description:
Super cute lasercut brooches, made in Australia by Scoops Designs.

The little wooden elephant is made from recycled plywood and the cat, apple and dachshund brooches are made from a lovely glossy perspex. All have a nickel backing.

name: Tin Spinning Top - Two Styles
description:
A good old fashioned spinning top is such a classic tin toy, they simply never go out of style.

Available in two cute designs, these sturdy tops hum gently as they spin, delighting and fascinating babies and little ones.

13cm diameter

name: Miniland Marbulous
description:
Marbulous lets kids design and build their very own marble run. They'll be entertained for hours, making new paths for the the marbles to take. Ideal for ages 4 - 6.  

38 pieces, box measures 26 x 37 x 8 cm

name: Blafre Drink Bottle
description:
Blafre stainless steel drink bottles are just too adorable for words. The Scandinavian designs are bright, colourful and fun. They're the perfect size too - 350ml - not too big, not too small.

Featuring a BPA free sports cap, these bottles won't leak in your bag. Hand wash only.

Recyclable packaging. Box measures 18 x 7 x 7 cm

name: Besties textas - 3 fun styles
description:
TEXTAS -Besties are a marker and a toy in one! The collectable character shapes make for a chunky grip that is easy to hold. The colours are vibrant, non-toxic and super washable. Plus, when the kids are done creating their latest masterpiece, they can use the figurines for imaginative play

3 designs to choose from:
fairytale
dino
pooch

name: Candy Matching Game
description:
Who needs real candy when you can have a candy memory game? This set includes 24 pairs to match, and don't worry, all your favourites are there - jellybeans, candy canes, all-sorts, lollipops and more!

Box measures 24 x 2 x 18 cm

best suited to 3+

name: Kid-O Blue Airplane
description:
Let your imagination soar with this gliding toddler plane. The dynamic rolling rubber wheels and spinning front propeller will engage your young pilot. Suitable for ages 1+

Packaged dimensions: 23 x 21 x 10.5 cm

name: Duns Jumpsuit - Dotflowers
description:
Duns of Sweden are never ones to shy away from bold prints. 
These full length jumpsuits are such a burst of happy colour, printed on 100% organic cotton (so soft), and manufactured Fair Trade.  

Featuring popper studs right down the legs, these excellent suits are great for daywear or sleepwear and make for easy peasy dressing.
Those clever Swedes. 

Please see below for available sizes

name: Memory Game - Alexander Girard
description:
Great memory game for the whole family, featuring bright and beautiful Alexander Girard illustrations. 

There are 36 pairs in total, but you can use less pairs for younger children. 

Suitable for ages 2+

Box measures 19.5 x 19.5 x 2.5 cm
